Package com.starsoft.plib.core.triggers

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CALLBACK_IN
    Constants that determine which thread the result will be returned in
    DELIVER_
    When passed as a "onProcessedCallback" in com.starsoft.plib.executors.SequentiallyProcessorExecutor.processing initiates the transfer of the task result to the next task
    NOT_NULL_DATA_STRATEGY
    Defines the strategy of behavior in case the task which takes the data from the previous task has a nonnull data
